# FAQ Section (.vasora)

components:
  - name: faq-accordion
    description: "Collapsible list of frequently asked questions with search/filter input."
    props:
      - items: array(title, content)

accessibility:
  - each accordion header implemented with button element and aria-expanded
  - content regions with aria-hidden toggled and role="region" plus aria-labelledby
  - keyboard: support Enter/Space to toggle, Up/Down to navigate between headers

assets-suggestions:
  - assets/vasora/icon-faq.svg

notes:
  - include micro-copy for support contact and expected response times
  - keep answers concise; link to deeper docs when appropriate
